---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="All Travel Articles | Slow Travel with Pankhuri and Kaushal"
  description="Browse our complete collection of travel experiences, opinions, and insights in one place."
>
  <main class="py-12 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-black">All Travel Articles</h1>
      
      <div class="mb-8">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
          <a href="/experiences" class="bg-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-primary-600 font-medium">
            Experiences
          </a>
          <a href="/opinions" class="bg-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-primary-600 font-medium">
            Opinions
          </a>
          <span class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md">
            All Articles
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 2025 -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-black border-b border-green-200 pb-2">2025</h2>
        
        <!-- March 2025 -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-black bg-green-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block">March 2025</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
            <!-- Mar 20 - Coldplay Concert -->
            <a href="/experiences/coldplay-concert-mumbai" class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300 no-underline">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-gray-200 relative">
                <img 
                  src="/images/experiences/coldplay/coldplay2.webp" 
                  srcset="/images/experiences/coldplay/coldplay2.webp 800w,
                          /images/experiences/coldplay/coldplay2-400w.webp 400w"
                  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 400px"
                  alt="Coldplay Concert in Mumbai" 
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  width="400" 
                  height="225"
                  loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Mar 20, 2025
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bg-green-500 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Experience
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">A Magical Night with Coldplay in Mumbai</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Our unforgettable experience at the Coldplay concert in DY Patil Stadium. From LED wristbands to incredible performances, it was truly one of the most magical evenings we've ever had.</p>
                <span class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </div>
            </a>
            
            <!-- Mar 18 - Slow Travel Article -->
            <a href="/opinions/slow-travel-reasons" class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300 no-underline">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <picture>
                  <source
                    srcset="/images/opinions/slow-travel-reasons/registan1-400w.webp 400w,
                           /images/opinions/slow-travel-reasons/registan1-800w.webp 800w"
                    sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 400px"
                    type="image/webp"
                  />
                  <img src="/images/opinions/slow-travel-reasons/registan1.webp" 
                    alt="Registan Square in Samarkand" 
                    class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                </picture>
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Mar 18, 2025
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bg-yellow-500 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Opinion
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">Why We Prefer Relatively Slow Travel</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Our perspective on the benefits of spending more time in fewer places rather than rushing to check destinations off a bucket list. How slow travel changed our perspective.</p>
                <span class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </div>
            </a>
            
            <!-- Mar 15 - Women's IPL Final -->
            <a href="/experiences/womens-ipl-final" class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300 no-underline">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-gray-200 relative">
                <img 
                  src="/images/experiences/womens-ipl-2025/image1.webp" 
                  srcset="/images/experiences/womens-ipl-2025/image1.webp 800w,
                          /images/experiences/womens-ipl-2025/image1-800w.webp 800w,
                          /images/experiences/womens-ipl-2025/image1-400w.webp 400w"
                  sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 400px"
                  alt="Women's IPL Final 2025" 
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                  width="400" 
                  height="225"
                  loading="lazy" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Mar 15, 2025
                </div>
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 bg-green-500 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Experience
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">Experiencing the Women's IPL Final in Mumbai</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Our exciting day at Brabourne Stadium watching the Women's IPL Final between Mumbai Indians and Delhi Capitals. The electric atmosphere and growing popularity of women's cricket made this a memorable experience.</p>
                <span class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 